  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified API for 10+ foundational time-series models",
    "Zero-shot forecasting and fine-tuning capabilities",
    "Support for forecasting, anomaly detection, classification, and imputation",
    "Comprehensive evaluation metrics (MSE, MAE, MASE, CRPS, etc.)",
    "Pre-trained model integration from HuggingFace",
    "Model quantization for efficient inference",
    "Built-in dataset loaders for common benchmarks"
